data.name: Label2.Text
data.value:
Fortran-It is a simple development environment (SDE) which enables the user to manage Fortran codes and compile them using the pre-installed Fortran compiler. Due to its simplicity, Fortran-It SDE aims to help Fortran programmers to write and compile their code efficiently.
Notes from the programmer: This SDE is initially designed and programmed by Rabie for free. I would like to thank those who supports me while writing this SDE kit.
